@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rdrlhv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.exp((0.74 / (v2 + 0.77 - v0 + 0.22)))
    v0 = wp.exp((0.51 / (tmp + 0.64 - v2 + 0.55)))
    v0 = v0
    v2 = 0.09
    tmp = (wp.exp(wp.cos(v2 + 0.54)) * (0.92 + 0.31))
    data[tid] = v0
